Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:10.12,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,10秒の猶予をやる
Dialogue: 90,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.04,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 90,0:00:10.97,0:00:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.05,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 90,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.71,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 90,0:00:14.73,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.50,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 90,0:00:16.38,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:18.97,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 90,0:00:18.05,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:20.60,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 90,0:00:19.57,0:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:22.69,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,出ていくしか…
Dialogue: 90,0:00:20.99,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to go out!
