Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:04.96,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何者だ
Dialogue: 90,0:02:03.84,0:02:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.79,TEXT JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いやそれより
Dialogue: 90,0:02:05.69,0:02:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, more importantly!
